cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.DS 

This paper is about learning to rank, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely category. The paper also uses deep Q-learning, which is a type of machine learning, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely categories as well. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) since it deals with ranking documents based on their relevance to a given query, making cs.CL a possible category. Finally, the paper involves data analysis and optimization, making cs.DS a possible category as well.
